# .gitignore — Search, Processing and Use of Information (PUBLIC repo)
#
# NOTE: Office formats (.xlsx/.pptx/.pdf/.docx) are NOT ignored here — they are
# the teaching content. This file blocks only junk, secrets, and — critically —
# any assessment or student-identifying material that must never become public.

# --- NEVER publish: assessment & student-identifying material ---
# These belong only in the private course repo. Listed so an accidental copy
# into this tree is refused rather than committed.
02-Assessments/
**/Submissions/
**/Peer Review/
**/Reports/
**/Video Presentations/
*Grades*.xlsx
*grade*.xlsx
*roster*
*peer_review*
# Labeled solution files (worked teaching examples are fine; graded solutions are not)
*Solution*.xlsx
*Solutions*.xlsx
*Solutions*.docx
* - Solution*.xlsx
*SOLVED*

# --- Secrets / credentials ---
*.env
.env*
*.key
*.pem
*.pfx
*secret*
*credential*
*token*

# --- OS / OneDrive / Office temp & lock files ---
~$*
*.tmp
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini

# --- Editor / IDE ---
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*~

# --- Build artifacts ---
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.log
.venv/
node_modules/
